Document: EditorExportPlatformExtension
Path: godot/classes/class_editorexportplatformextension.rst
Summary: Describes the EditorExportPlatformExtension class, which external export platform implementations should inherit from.

Description
External EditorExportPlatform implementations should inherit from this class.

To use EditorExportPlatform, register it using the EditorPlugin.add_export_platform() method first.
